    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3083360/extras/0b8fcc6d891cb6ebfd36197d09c0d897.poster.avif?t=1759060948\" width=600 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3083360/extras/0b8fcc6d891cb6ebfd36197d09c0d897.webm?t=1759060948\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3083360/extras/0b8fcc6d891cb6ebfd36197d09c0d897.mp4?t=1759060948\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><strong>在在这款星际角色扮演游戏中，一个神秘的漩涡将地球及其居民变成了拼图！扮演最后一只幸存的青蛙 Frogus，穿越太空中的浮动平台，与敌人战斗并收集拼图碎片。拯救你的青蛙同伴，解开五彩漩涡的秘密，重建地球！</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3083360/extras/a13bb4551f4717e918b727b37ada3549.poster.avif?t=1759060948\" width=630 height=186 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3083360/extras/a13bb4551f4717e918b727b37ada3549.webm?t=1759060948\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3083360/extras/a13bb4551f4717e918b727b37ada3549.mp4?t=1759060948\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>🐸每次闯关都要探索关卡、外星敌人和完全随机生成的环境。每次冒险都是独一无二的，青蛙每次跃入太空都会有惊喜。🌠</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3083360/extras/e5481e3a0610190864224e8e938947bf.poster.avif?t=1759060948\" width=630 height=186 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3083360/extras/e5481e3a0610190864224e8e938947bf.webm?t=1759060948\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3083360/extras/e5481e3a0610190864224e8e938947bf.mp4?t=1759060948\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>✨ 随着等级的提升，您的卡牌也会随之升级，每成功通关一关，您就能解锁新的卡牌，让您的力量更加多样化，击溃敌人！✨ </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3083360/extras/1eaf82b01915975d9af093d6d5c07967.poster.avif?t=1759060948\" width=630 height=186 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3083360/extras/1eaf82b01915975d9af093d6d5c07967.webm?t=1759060948\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3083360/extras/1eaf82b01915975d9af093d6d5c07967.mp4?t=1759060948\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>👊史诗般的太空战斗！保卫弗洛格斯，抵御外星入侵者！ 👽 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3083360/extras/1941b162fe888a6e4d24c367b6a4f007.avif?t=1759060948\" width=600 height=150 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >________________________________________________________________________________________________________</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3083360/extras/e5d1c57df0e4f4ef18d7ec888f3ab908.avif?t=1759060948\" width=631 height=94 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
